    <item>
      <title>联合利华印度公司利润因消费需求低迷而令人失望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/unilever-india-s-profit-misses-estimate-on-weak-consumer-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度斯坦联合利华有限公司公布的季度利润表现不佳，原因是印度炎热夏季消费需求低迷以及通货膨胀上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/unilever-india-s-profit-misses-estimate-on-weak-consumer-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 10:24:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度提高税收以抑制股票交易中的零售狂热</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/india-to-hike-capital-gains-tax-in-setback-for-stock-market-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度几十年来首次对股票投资和股票衍生品收益税做出重大修改，试图抑制该国 5 万亿美元市场的投机交易激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/india-to-hike-capital-gains-tax-in-setback-for-stock-market-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 07:13:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士宝盛任命高盛资深人士布林格为新任首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/julius-baer-picks-goldman-sachs-veteran-bollinger-as-new-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士宝盛集团有限公司 (Julius Baer Group Ltd) 已聘请斯蒂芬·博林格 (Stefan Bollinger) 担任其下一任首席执行官，对于这家瑞士财富管理公司而言，这是一个相对不为人知的选择，该公司正试图摆脱去年的 Signa 房地产丑闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/julius-baer-picks-goldman-sachs-veteran-bollinger-as-new-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 05:17:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
